'''Faṭima Mrnisi''' (1940 - 2015) tga yat tamarat [[Lmɣrib|tamɣribit]] ar ttara f tasnamunt d timɣarin.<ref>https://archive.org/details/beyondveilmalefe0000mern</ref>

== Tudrt nns ==
Tlul ɣ 27 Ctmbr 1940 ɣ [[Fas]] gr mnanw n tmɣarin lli illan dar jddas. Tɣra dar [[Fransa|ifransiyn]] lliɣ umzn [[Lmɣrib]].

Tda s [[Fṛansa|Fransa]] ɣ 1957 afad ad tɣr tsrtit ɣ Surbun d ɣinn nit aɣ tga tadukturt.

Lliɣ turri s [[Lmɣrib]] ar tsaqra tasnamunt ɣ taɣiwant n tskla zɣ 1947 ar 1981.

